cc:Work.dc:title: Three Men in a Boat
cc:Work.dc:description: I love rescuing potentially useful drawings from the dustbins of history! This drawing of (yup, you guessed it!) three men in a (yup) boat was drawn way back in 1911, about a 100 years ago. And now if anyone wants three men in a boat, it is available for the future. Hurrah!
